data.title: 1961 Press Photo Dr. Robert Hofstadter, Nobel Prize winner for Physics.
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. Shares Nobel Prize: Dr. Robert Hofstadter (above), of Stanford University, California, and Rudolf L. Moessbauer, of Munich, now working as a guest at California Institute of Technology, Pasadena, California, were awarded the Nobel Prize for Physics.
